Introduction

PAPAYA was a short-lived five-member girl group under their label One Star Music and agency Winsome Media with their debut studio album Fairy Tale. They debuted on August 16, 2000, with their first full album “Fairy Tale”. Kyunga and Yoonmi left the group on December 9th, 2001. The group officially disbanded in 2001 but had a one-off reunion in 2016.
